high_descs: Turn around and walk to the trash can.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll next to the trash can.
Approach the the toilet on your left.
Place the toilet paper roll on the toilet.
Turn to your right and approach the trash can.
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the trash can.
Turn to your left and walk to the toilet.
Place the toilet paper roll on the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place an empty and a full toilet paper roll on the toilet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the dresser, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up toilet paper tube that is on the ground to the right of the red bin.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn around to face the toilet.
Put the toilet paper toilet on the front left corner of the toilet tank.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and walk towards the tub, turn right to face the counter.
Pick up the toilet paper roll out of the red bin.
Turn right and walk forward, then turn left and walk up to the counter, turn left again to face the toilet.
Put the toilet paper roll on top of the toilet tank behind the toilet paper tube.
anns.task_desc: Move toilet paper tubes to the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the space between the toilet and the sink.
Pick up the tube to the right of the red container.
Move to face the back of the toilet.
Place the tube on the left edge of the back of the toilet.
Move to face the space between the toilet and the sink.
Pick up the toilet paper roll from the red bin on the floor.
Move to face the back of the toilet.
Place the roll of toilet paper on the back of the toilet and behind the tube.
anns.task_desc: To move a tube and roll of toilet paper to the back of the toilet.
